filtersOut: filters out some technical entries - details see help
urlToUserpage: URL to section or subsection (#) of your user page.
tooltipSearch: page title (e.g. Hollywood). You may also use wildcards "*", e.g. Hollywood* or User:Tom* .See help for further details.
searchOnlyTOP: This search was performed only in TOP lists.
mycontribsOptin: This feature makes use of X!'s editcounter opt-in model. Without opt-in, the readout is limited to namespace 0 (article) and a lowest possible edit limit of $1.
optInOAuth: Alternatively you can login with Wikimedia OAuth
onlyOwnCreatedPages: show only pages I have created
historyDataCatchup: Notice: history data is in catching-up process
selectCategory: Select your category from the left menu
homeMain: Home is the main data table which contains any data
filerResults: Filter the results by changing the parameters in the top menu as you like
optinMsg1: User has not yet opted in. If you want to see graphs, please create $1 with any content
optinMsg2: Alternatively, you can create $1 on Meta-Wiki to opt-in across all Wikimedia wikis.
authorMostEdits: Author with most edits. In German Wikpedia: Author with largest text share
statsEntry: $1 - Page view and page popularity statistics with Top 100,000 hit lists for all Wikimedia wiki's (today, per month and custom time periods). Additional features: Wildcard search, 24-hour statistics, personal favorites, global project totals, support for disambiguation pages and Wikidata items. Hourly updates.
